scenes.description: Nanashi Mumei discusses the ancient civilization and discovery of a skull, revealing she might have left it there herself as a 'secret stash'.
Transition sequence with scenic views of the ruins and the surrounding forest.
Nanashi Mumei performs the song 'Call your name'.
